data.description: Welcome home! Must see barely lived in townhome boasts three well-appointed bedrooms, each offering a tranquil sanctuary for rest and relaxation. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a private en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet.  Step inside and be greeted by an inviting ambiance that combines contemporary elegance with comfortable living spaces. The open floor plan features a perfect setting for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring high-end appliances, sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. One of the standout features of this townhome is the private patio oasis, a serene outdoor space where you can unwind, sip your morning coffee, or indulge in a good book. As a resident of Trinity Falls, you'll have access to an array of amenities that enhance your quality of life.
